      <title>英国暴乱罪名成立后 YouTube 上仇恨视频仍在流传</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/youtube-hate-video-remained-up-even-after-uk-riot-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月 5 日晚，亚伦·约翰逊抵达英格兰北部斯托克波特的不列颠尼亚酒店。这位来自附近地区的 32 岁男子来这里是为了看看他所说的“移民酒店”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/youtube-hate-video-remained-up-even-after-uk-riot-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划在越南举行联合演习后开展更多海上活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-plans-more-sea-activities-with-vietnam-after-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾海岸警卫队表示，菲律宾和越南本周在存在海上争端的情况下举行了联合演习，海岸警卫队计划今年晚些时候派遣一艘船前往越南，以加强海上合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-plans-more-sea-activities-with-vietnam-after-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 01:35:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前往中东的美国航母上的水兵做好冲突准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/sailors-on-us-carrier-headed-for-middle-east-brace-for-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当亚伯拉罕·林肯号航空母舰撤出关岛时，该航空母舰的船长通过对讲机向船员宣布，美国对中东地区胡塞导弹和无人机发动的新一轮打击“提醒了我们将要面临的环境”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/sailors-on-us-carrier-headed-for-middle-east-brace-for-conflict</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
